sub_title: Mind and wisdom based inspiration for happiness and success in life and business
summary: From Ambition to Meaning. After a successful corporate career (1995 - 2019) in Finance with Shell, now ready to inspire children, adults and businesses to be happy and successful. During our time in Singapore, we found a treasure: the best meditation (mind) and life skill training and coaching programs of Asia, developed by Vikas Malkani, the number 1 wisdom coach in the world. As meditation and life skill teachers, certified by Vikas, with Mind ur Life we are now bringing these trademarked programs to the Netherlands to help you grow your lives and businesses.
